To fill view cells: view of i32 with value: i32.
For each index i of cells: cells at i becomes value.

To sum view cells: view of i32, giving i32.
Let total be 0.
For each index i of cells: total becomes total plus cells at i.
Give total.

To main, giving i32.
Let cells be buffer of 4 i32 filled with 0.
Let middle be view of cells from 1 for 2.
fill view middle with 7.
Give sum view cells.
